PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FThis was followed by 12 weeks of
OL,7,Fintensive neuro rehabilitation, which
OL,8,Fsaw her go from being unable to speak,
OL,9,Feat or move, to getting her life back
OL,10,Fand enjoying every minute with her
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,FHer parents Jude Pender, 40, and
OL,14,FAndrew Macrae, 43, first noticed
OL,15,F"worrying changes" in Jessica's health
OL,16,Fin the summer of 2025.
OL,18,F"What started as headaches and feeling
OL,19,Fsick in the mornings gradually
OL,20,Fprogressed to problems with balance
OL,21,Fand coordination," Ms Pender said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]zD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,F"It was very incremental, but there
OL,7,Fwere lots of things that didn't feel
OL,8,Fright.
OL,10,F"Her colouring in went from being fine
OL,11,Ffor her age to very messy, she
OL,12,Fdisengaged from gymnastics because she
OL,13,Fsaid it made her dizzy, and I noticed
OL,14,Fher walk had changed."
OL,16,FAfter an initial visit to Accident and
OL,17,FEmergency in August and several GP
OL,18,Fappointments, Jessica's parents
OL,19,Freturned to the RHC in October when
OL,20,Fher symptoms worsened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FA CT scan revealed a mass at the back
OL,7,Fof Jessica's brain, along with a
OL,8,Fbuildup of fluid.
OL,10,F"When the neurosurgeon came to speak
OL,11,Fto us, we knew it was serious," Ms
OL,12,FPender said. "We were told Jessica
OL,13,Fwould need surgery immediately."
OL,15,FJessica underwent surgery on October
OL,16,F17, and following a short stay in
OL,17,Fintensive care she was transferred to
OL,18,Fa ward.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@_O]tD@NOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
