CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FHer recovery was initially extremely
OL,7,Fchallenging, with little movement or
OL,8,Fresponsiveness, and severe sickness,
OL,9,Fso medics took the decision to fit a
OL,10,F"shunt" to drain excess fluid.
OL,12,FAlthough Jessica began to stabilise,
OL,13,Fshe was unable to move or speak and
OL,14,Frequired a feeding tube.
OL,16,FShe also needed full assistance from
OL,17,Ftwo staff members for any movement.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FMs Pender continued: "The
OL,7,Fneurosurgeons did a great job with
OL,8,FJessica to get her to that point, and
OL,9,Fwe are so grateful to them for saving
OL,10,Fher life.
OL,12,F"We also knew that it would take a
OL,13,Fteam following the surgery to progress
OL,14,Fher movement, but we were never sure
OL,15,Fwhat the outcome would be."
OL,17,FMs Pender credited the intensive
OL,18,Fneurorehabilitation Jessica then
OL,19,Freceived with the RHC physiotherapy
OL,20,Fteam for progressing her recovery to
OL,21,Fwhere she is today.
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
