OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FJessica remained in hospital for 13
OL,7,Fweeks, with daily physiotherapy
OL,8,Fsessions taking place at her bedside,
OL,9,Fin the sensory room, gym and
OL,10,Fhydrotherapy pool.
OL,12,F"At the beginning, her rehabilitation
OL,13,Fwas like fasttracking a baby's
OL,14,Fdevelopment, learning to hold her head
OL,15,Fup, sit, crawl, eat and walk again,"
OL,16,FMs Pender said.
OL,18,F"Her main physio, Fiona (Norval),
OL,19,Ftailored every session to what Jessica
OL,20,Fenjoyed.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@dO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
