CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,F"They played games, set up obstacle
OL,7,Fcourses and made everything feel fun.
OL,8,FJessica looked forward to her physio,
OL,9,Fand that made such a difference."
OL,11,FJessica was discharged in January and
OL,12,Fis continuing her recovery.
OL,14,FHer speech has returned, she is eating
OL,15,Findependently, her motor skills have
OL,16,F"significantly improved", and she is
OL,17,Fnow able to walk with more stability
OL,18,Fand confidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]xD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,FShe is now looking forward to
OL,7,Fcelebrating her fifth birthday in
OL,8,FApril, with a fun-filled trip to a
OL,9,Ffarm park with her cousins.
OL,11,FThis is something her parents feared
OL,12,Fmight not be possible just six months
OL,13,Fearlier.
OL,15,F"Jessica is such a happy little girl
OL,16,Fand has shown incredible resilience
OL,17,Fand determination," Ms Pender said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,F"She knows she has been unwell, but I
OL,7,Fdon't think she realises just how far
OL,8,Fshe has come. We are so incredibly
OL,9,Fgrateful to the teams who cared for
OL,10,Fher."
OL,12,FFiona Norval, a paediatric
OL,13,Fphysiotherapist with NHS Greater
OL,14,FGlasgow and Clyde, said Jessica's
OL,15,Fdetermination throughout her recovery
OL,16,Fhad been "incredible to see".
OL,18,F"Her rehabilitation was intensive and
OL,19,Fchallenging, but she approached every
OL,20,Fsession with curiosity and
OL,21,Fenthusiasm," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]xD@JOUxD@\O]zD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777007079
OL,3,CMother 'so incredibly grateful' to
OL,4,Cmedics for saving daughter's life
OL,6,F"Our aim in paediatric physiotherapy
OL,7,Fis always to make therapy engaging and
OL,8,Fmeaningful for the child, and
OL,9,FJessica's progress is a testament to
OL,10,Fher hard work, her family's support
OL,11,Fand the dedication of the wider
OL,12,Fmultidisciplinary team involved in her
OL,13,Fcare."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
